openspec/changes/**/evidence.md

# Dead-code cleanup loop quarantine (local-only, retrievable)
/.trash/
.trash-cleanup-worknotes.md
# /loop session output (local-only, not shared)
/.ai/

# IDE / editor personal config (per-machine, not shared)
.vscode/
.idea/
.fleet/
# Merge/rebase leftovers
*.orig
*.bak
